     <h2>II. Committee Report on Gunpowder Sent to the Northern Army</h2>
     
     <div class="docbody">
      <div class="opener">
       <table class="salutationBlock">
        <tr>
		<td class="salutationRight">
        [<ins title="editorial addition or explanation" class="ed">post 16 Oct. 1775</ins>]
        <a class="ptr" href="#PJA03d083n1" id="PJA03d083n1-ptr">1</a>
       </td>
	      </tr>
      </table>
      </div>
      <p>The Committee appointed to enquire, what Powder has been Sent to the Army in the Northern Department, have attended that service and beg Leave to report</p>
      <table class="bodytext" id="PJA03d083t1">
     <tr>
	      <td class="par">That five Thousand Weight of Powder, sent from South Carolina, has been forwarded to the said Army.</td>
	      <td class="curr frac" style="vertical-align: bottom;">5000 wt.</td>
	    </tr>
     <tr class="pb_row">
	      <td title="page number in print edition" id="ADMS-06-03-02-pb-0140" colspan="2"><span class="pb center" title="page number in print edition" id="ADMS-06-03-02-pb-0140">[140<a style="padding-left: 0px" onclick="window.open('/img-document-get.xqy?image=ADMS/Pages/ADMS-06-03/ADMS-06-03-02-pb-0140.jpg', 'pageImage', 'scrollbars=1,resizable=1'); return false" onkeypress="this.onclick();" tabindex="0" title="Click to view image of page from print edition"><img src="/img-ML/page-icon.gif" width="18" height="20" style="vertical-align:middle;" alt="page icon"/></a>]</span></td>
	    </tr>
     <tr>
	      <td class="par">That Two Thousand one hundred and thirty six Pounds Weight have been forwarded to the Same Army from the City of Philadelphia.</td>
	      <td class="curr" style="vertical-align: bottom;">2136</td>
	    </tr>
     <tr>
	      <td class="par">That Seventeen hundred Weight have been forwarded from New York.</td>
	      <td class="curr" style="vertical-align: bottom;">1700</td>
	    </tr>
     <tr>
	      <td class="par">That Eight hundred Weight has been forwarded from Connecticutt.</td>
	      <td class="curr" style="vertical-align: bottom;">800</td>
	    </tr>
     <tr>
	      <td class="par">That Thirteen hundred Weight has been forwarded at another Time from the City of Philadelphia.</td>
	      <td class="curr" style="vertical-align: bottom; border-bottom: 1px solid black;">1300</td>
	    </tr>
     <tr>
	      <td></td>
	      <td class="curr" style="vertical-align: bottom;">10936</td>
	    </tr>
     <tr>
	      <td class="par">In Addition to which Two thousand Weight has been lately ordered to New York and from there to the same Army.<a class="ptr" href="#PJA03d083n2" id="PJA03d083n2-ptr">2</a></td>
	      <td class="curr" style="vertical-align: bottom; border-bottom: 1px solid black;">2000</td>
	    </tr>
     <tr>
	      <td></td>
	      <td class="curr" style="vertical-align: bottom;">12,936</td>
	    </tr>
    </table>
   </div>
     <div class="docback">
      <div class="note-source" id="PJA03d083sn1">
       
   <p>
        <span class="docSource"><span class="dType">MS in <abbr title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ John Adams (17351826) ]">JA</abbr>s hand</span> (<span class="ref-terms">Adams Papers, Microfilms</span>, Reel No. 346, filmed under date [17761778]).</span>
       </p>

      </div>
      <div id="fn" class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#PJA03d083n1-ptr" id="PJA03d083n1">1</a>
       
   <p>On 16 Oct. a committee composed of John Langdon, Eliphalet Dyer, and <abbr title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ John Adams (17351826) ]">JA</abbr> was ordered to make a survey of the amounts of gunpowder sent to the northern army and by whom. The Journals do not record any report made or accepted (<span class="ref-st" title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ Worthington C. Ford and others, eds., &lt;i&gt;Journals of the Continental Congress&lt;/i&gt;, 17741789, Washington, 19041937; 34 vols. ]"><span class="hi-italic" style="font-style: italic;">JCC</span></span>, 3:296).</p>

      </div>
      <div class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#PJA03d083n2-ptr" id="PJA03d083n2">2</a>
       
   <p>Pres. Hancock informed Gen. Schuyler of the shipment of powder in his letter of 11 Oct. (<span class="ref-st" title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ Edmund C. Burnett, ed., &lt;i&gt;Letters of Members of the Continental Congress&lt;/i&gt;, Washington, 19211936; 8 vols. ]">Burnett, ed., <span class="hi-italic" style="font-style: italic;">Letters of Members</span></span>, 1:228).</p>

      </div>
     </div>
